Name: MyBot
About the game: Help Mybot find his home through a 3d maze of traps. Beware of shuttering glass, sliding ice, blocking walls and reset traps. Challenge yourself or your friend in multi-player. Have hours of fun and never run out of game-play as you create your own levels. Make your game the cool place to go.
